title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show OCT-23-2013 WED
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show OCT-23-2013 WED








Dennis Prager Radio Show
Prager 20131023  3 Raven Never More

Prager H3: The Baltimore Ravens have been recruited to promote ObamaCare.
 To the Left, no area of life is allowed to be free of their politics
 Dennis talks to Paul Marshall, 
  Senior Fellow at Center for Religious Freedom at the Hudson Institute about
    the persecution of Christians around the world.




Prager 20131023  2 Male/Female Hour: Who Changes?

Prager H2: Who changes more after marriage .. the husband or the wife?





Prager 20131023  1 Shrinking Governor

Prager H1: Ohio Governor, John Kasich, is pushing Ohio into ObamaCare
  over the objections of his own Republican legislature
   Dennis talks to John Alford, associate professor of political science
    at Rice University.
 His new book is 

     Predisposed: Liberals, Conservatives, and the Biology of Political Differences.
